markdownRemark.html: Kate lives in North Wales with her cat Geralt and has been a passionate gamer since the mid 80s when she first came into possession of a ZX Spectrum. Her game of choice is Elite Dangerous. When she’s not gaming or streaming she works for LGBT+ charity Diversity Role Models.
